reviewText: Pretty good. Your husband will love any of the moves you can pick up.

The instructor is not so great.
Every choreography is short and easy but little challenges.
It's nice for beginners.

Choreographies are:
Cheerleader
Cowgirl
East Meets West
Maid
Naughty Nurse
with music from "Strip To It Fantasy".

You can watch sample movies on striptoit.com.
It's fun!
